SUMMARY:FREE Tummy Time Class
DESCRIPTION:Come join our free Tummy Time Class\, every Tuesday from 1:00-2:00pm at Davis Parent Nursery School. The goal of this meetup is to provide a space for parents with newborns to connect with other parents from the community. Moms\, Dads\, and all caretakers welcome. Siblings are not able to join at this time. We are here to support YOU and your baby! No pre-registration needed\, simply show up. Led by our wonderful teacher\, Annie Ramirez. \n  \nThis program will be ongoing through the school year\, except for school breaks.
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/free-tummy-time-class-4/2026-04-07/
LOCATION:Davis Parent Nursery School (8th Street)\, 426 West 8th Street\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
